<% content_for :page_title do %>
  Pick a session
<% end %>

<article role="article" class="group">
  <div class="inner-block text">
    <p><mark>You will get the same thing out of both</mark></p>
    <p><mark>You can choose one or the other</mark></p>
    <p><mark>You can only have one</mark></p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-wrapper">
    <div class="grid grid-1-2">
      <div class="inner-block">
        <h2>Face to face</h2>

        <p>
          You’ll need to travel to a local guidance branch (up to 1 hour).
          Your session will be <mark>within 4 weeks</mark> of you making the booking.
        </p>

        <p><mark>F2F sessions are with an advisor from CitA</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You book an appointment and then visit that office</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You will receive an email or SMS reminder</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You will need to pick up</mark></p>
        <p><mark>The appointment will last upto 45 minutes</mark></p>

        <form action="/appointments/face-to-face/search" method="get" class="form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-bold" for="full-name">Postcode</label>
            <p class="form-hint">Enter a postcode to find the nearest branch.</p>
            <input type="text" class="form-control-1-8" id="postcode" name="postcode">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group get-started">
            <input type="submit" class="big button" value="Find a local branch">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-1-2">
      <div class="inner-block">
        <h2>Phone</h2>

        <p>Your session will be <mark>within 5 days</mark> of you making the booking.</p>

        <p><mark>Phone appointments are with an advisor from TPAS</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You book an appointment and we will call you on the appointed date and time</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You will receive an email or SMS reminder</mark></p>
        <p><mark>You will need to pick up</mark></p>
        <p><mark>The appointment will last upto 45 minutes</mark></p>

        <p class="get-started">
          <a rel="nofollow" href="/appointments/phone/availability" class="big button">Book a phone session</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="inner-block text">
    <h2>What you’ll need for your session</h2>
    <p>To get the most out of your session you'll need some information
      beforehand. This will help our experts to prepare and it will save time
      during the session. </p>

    <p>You'll need to have ready:</p>

    <ul class="list-bullet">
      <li>the value of your pension pots</li>
      <li>other income you have, eg from work, property, investments</li>
      <li>your pension statements</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</article>
